hifiberry-librespot (0.6.0.8) stable; urgency=low

  * Enhanced startup script with Avahi daemon availability check
  * Added 30-second wait for Avahi to become responsive when using Avahi mDNS backend
  * Improved reliability during system startup with proper service dependency handling
  * Added explicit --mdns-backend parameter to librespot command line options
  * Enhanced error reporting for mDNS functionality issues

 -- HiFiBerry <info@hifiberry.com>  Fri, 04 Jul 2025 16:00:00 +0000

